sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Master as Master DB
    participant Replica as Replica DB

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
    Note over Client,Replica: T=0s: Create Product
    Client->>API: POST /api/products<br/>{name: "iPhone"}
    API->>Master: INSERT (id=101)
    Master-->>API: Success
    API-->>Client: Created (id=101)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 230)
    Note over Client,Replica: T=0.5s: Read from Replica (TOO EARLY!)
    Client->>API: GET /api/products/101
    API->>Replica: SELECT WHERE id=101
    Replica-->>API: NOT FOUND ❌
    API-->>Client: 404 Not Found
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
    Note over Client,Replica: T=0.5s: Read from Master (SUCCESS!)
    Client->>API: GET /api/products/101/from-master
    API->>Master: SELECT WHERE id=101
    Master-->>API: Product found ✅
    API-->>Client: 200 OK {product data}
    end

    rect rgb(240, 240, 255)
    Note over Master,Replica: T=2s: Replication Completes
    Master->>Replica: Replicate INSERT (id=101)
    Note over Replica: Product now available
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
    Note over Client,Replica: T=3s: Read from Replica (SUCCESS!)
    Client->>API: GET /api/products/101
    API->>Replica: SELECT WHERE id=101
    Replica-->>API: Product found ✅
    API-->>Client: 200 OK {product data}
    end
